efficiency: HIGH
time complexity: O(log N) for update, O(1) for current, O(log N) amortized for maximum and minimum
space complexity: O(N)
energy implications: MEDIUM
explanation: Uses a dictionary for direct price storage and lazy heaps to maintain min/max efficiently. The lazy set tracks outdated entries, allowing O(log N) amortized updates and queries.

